msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/guides/maintenance/hostname.rst:28
msgid "This example sets the hostname to *telemetry-test-2-h15*, to identify a |CL| telemetry test machine on the second floor at grid location H15. Make sure to reboot after setting a new hostname."
